%1.name
=======
- wait for tank to talk to and attack the boss
- [shatter spears] cast sends projectiles out of the spears
    in the ground
- stormforged obliterator add spawns. Interrupt [surge] and kill add
- [radiant tempest] cast, get out of the circle, 1 shot mechanic
- [runic brand] cast, go find the rune on the floor that matches the one
    on your head
- save cool downs for after [runic brand], once you are the angel form
    you get a damage buff